(4, 'Ceras', 'ceras.jpg', 'ceras_mini.jpg', '', '', '', 'Ceras varias (cervical, de modelar, para microfesados, colados, paralelizar, incrustaciones o de pegar ... )', NULL, '<table width="400" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td><h3>CERA CERVICAL</H3>\r\n            <p>Resultando superficies interiores uniformes, homog&eacute;neas y grosores iguales de   cera en las coronas.</p>\r\n    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td width="41%">Color rojo (1)</td>\r\n          <td width="25%">100 g</td>\r\n          <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:130020</div></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <hr noshade="NOSHADE" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n    <h3>CERA DE MODELAR</h3>\r\n  <p>Especialmente para la aplicaci&oacute;n y modelaci&oacute;n monocolor en la  t&eacute;cnica de coronas y puentes.</p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="39%">Color azul royal (3)</td>\r\n      <td width="31%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="30%"><div align="right">Ref.:130021</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Color verde (2)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:130022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Color marfil (4)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126021</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Color azul claro </td>\r\n      <td>100 g -Plastificada- </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Color verde </td>\r\n      <td>100 g -Plastificada- </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Color gris claro (5)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:130023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CERA PARA MICROFRESADOS</h3>\r\n  <p>Excelentes propiedades para trabajos de microfresados raspado con paralel&oacute;metro o fresadora. Alta transparencia facilita un control continuo del grosor de la cera. </p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="47%">Color azul oscuro (6)</td>\r\n      <td width="19%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CERA PARA COLADOS</h3>\r\n  <p>Excelentes propiedades de modelado para la t&eacute;cnica de esquel&eacute;ticos. Ideal para la reuni&oacute;n de todas las ceras y piezas prefabricadas de pl&aacute;stico.. </p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="46%">Color azul (7)</td>\r\n      <td width="20%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133024</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CERA PARA PARALELIZAR</h3>\r\n  <p>Adecuado especialmente para paralelizar &aacute;ngulos muertos y relleno de cavidades de mu&ntilde;ones. Tiene un punto de fusi&oacute;n muy alto, es muy dura y acepta muy bien las lacas espaciadoras.</p>\r\n  <table width="98%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="40%">Color p&uacute;rpura (8)</td>\r\n      <td width="26%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CERA PARA INCRUSTACIONES </h3>\r\n  <p>Ajustada en sus propiedades..Especialmente elaborada para la fabricaci&oacute;n de incrustaciones como Inlays - Onlays, Coronas medias y Tres cuartos. Excelente precisi&oacute;n de ajuste y estabilidad de forma. </p>\r\n  <table width="98%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="41%">Color verde (9)</td>\r\n      <td width="25%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133021</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CERA DE PEGAR</h3>\r\n  <p>Alta adherencia, muy dura pero no quebradiza, quemando sin dejar residuos y optima eliminaci&oacute;n con agua caliente.</p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="41%">Color marfil (10)</td>\r\n      <td width="25%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133020</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n    </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </table>', 'Waxes', '', 'Waxes (cervical, modelling, milling, casting, blocking out, inlay, sticking...)', NULL, '<table width="400" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td><h3>CERVICAL - WAX</H3>\r\n            <p>Ideal for precision fit crown margins. Minimal soldification shrinkage. Adapts very well. </p>\r\n    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td width="41%">Red (1)</td>\r\n          <td width="25%">100 g</td>\r\n          <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:130020</div></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <hr noshade="NOSHADE" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n    <h3>MODELLING - WAX </h3>\r\n    <p>Special all-round modelling wax for crowns and bridges technique.</p>\r\n    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="39%">Kingblue (3)</td>\r\n      <td width="31%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="30%"><div align="right">Ref.:130021</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Green (2)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:130022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Ivory (4)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126021</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Lightblue </td>\r\n      <td>100 g -Plastified- </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Green </td>\r\n      <td>100 g -Plastified- </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:126023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Lightgrey (5)</td>\r\n      <td>100 g </td>\r\n      <td><div align="right">Ref.:130023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>MILLING- WAX</h3>\r\n  <p>Specially milling- and curving wax for hand modelling and milling machines. Very   hard and highly transparente for a better control of wax thickness.</p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="47%">Darkblue (6)</td>\r\n      <td width="19%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133023</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>CASTING - WAX </h3>\r\n  <p>Excelent modelling properties for the modell casting technique. Ideal for all wax unions and preformed plastic parts unions.</p>\r\n  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="46%">Blue (7)</td>\r\n      <td width="20%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133024</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <hr noshade="noshade" color="#E6E6E6" id="regla"/>\r\n  <h3>BLOCKING OUR - WAX </h3>\r\n  <p>Special wax for blocking out cavities and rough surfaces. Very high melting point and extremely hard. Accept very well die spacers.</p>\r\n  <table width="98%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td width="40%">Purple (8)</td>\r\n      <td width="26%">100 g </td>\r\n      <td width="34%"><div align="right">Ref.:133022</div></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  