(20, 'Líquidos', 'eco_pol_1000ml.jpg', 'eco_pol_1000ml_mini.jpg', '', '', '', 'Agente reductor de tensiones superficiales', 'ECOPOL', '<table width="400" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td><h3>Agente reductor de tensiones superficiales para todos los revestimientos de fosfato y escayola.</h3>\r\n    <p>Para la t&eacute;cnica de colados. ECOPOL crea un puente molecular entre la cera y el revestimiento produciendo as&iacute; una mejor fluidez y adaptaci&oacute;n del revestimiento a la cera.</p>\r\n    <p>ECOPOL produce colados lisos y libres de burbujas. Apropiado tambi&eacute;n para vaciados de impresiones de silicona.</p>\r\n    <p>ECOPOL no contiene productos disolventes de cera. No influye al fraguado de revestimiento ni a la dureza superficial de revestimientos de escayolas.    </p>\r\n    <p>1000 ml con botella pulverizador. </p>\r\n    <table width="98%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td><div align="right">Ref.:121 00 15 </div></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </table>', 'Liquids', '', 'Established wetting agent', NULL, '<table width="400" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td><h3><strong><span lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB">Established wetting agent for phosphatic and gypseous compounds</span></strong>.</h3>\r\n          <p>For an acurate clean cast. Wax degreasing and wax surface relaxing.\r\n\r\nECOPOL creates a molecular bridge between the water repellent wax\r\n\r\nand the compound. Adapts easily and bubble-free over the wax object.\r\n\r\nThis results in an acurate and smooth cast surface.</p>\r\n    <p>ECOPOL is also suitable as wetting agent for silicone and polyether moulds and gypsum cast models.</p>\r\n    <p>Free of formaldehyde, alcohol and liquified petroleum gas (LPG).</p>\r\n    <p>Set: 1000ml bottle with empty pump spray bottle.</p>\r\n    <table width="98%" border="0"